dc_title_s: Venezuela, approaches to Bahía Bergantín, Bahía Guanta and Bahía de Pertigalete (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours. "From U.S. charts to 1984." Place names in Spanish with glossary in English. "Copyright 1994 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Map No.24435. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
